captions.text:
Oh, you got pass--
all right. Come on.

But we had
to tell you how much
we enjoyed the show,

We're not mental
or anything,
so don't be afraid.

My name is wayne,
and this is garth.

So do you...
Come to milwaukee
often?

Well, I'm a regular
visitor here,

But milwaukee has certainly
had its share of visitors.

Were coming here as early
as the late 1600s

To trade with
the native americans.

Which is algonquin
for the good land.

I was not aware
of that.

One of the most
interesting aspects
of milwaukee

Is the fact that it's
the only major american city

To have ever elected
three socialist mayors.

Does this guy
know how to party
or what?

O.K. Well, we got
to get going.

No. Stick around.
Hang out with us.

Cool. Yeah,
we'll stay and
hang around with youse...

title: Wayne's World (8/10) Movie CLIP - Alice's History Lesson (1992) HD
